{"tid":584053,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過收到財仔追數信?","createTime":"2018-03-07T13:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T14:44:25.000Z","uid":3186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a33296f476e40d5c9795f2bfa08c19477389e3bc","tid":584053,"uid":3186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T13:53:26.000Z","msg":"唔知開咩台好, 當學術討論下<br />\n<br />\n話說今日屋企收到封財仔信<br />\n信面寫住欠債還錢天公地道一堆字<br />\n跟住我老豆就好燥咁開咗嚟睇<br />\n睇到一個唔識嘅印傭借左三千五百蚊無還到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我成家都唔識佢, 亦都唔知點解會寫咗我屋企地址<br />\n我老豆嬲到掉撚咗封信, 我頭先靜靜雞keep住咗<br />\n<br />\n無直接接觸過印傭<br />\n係十年前請過菲傭(我諗應該唔關事掛)<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打遇過類似經歷?<br />\n應該點做好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老老豆豆有啲淆底<br />\n唔係驚佢上嚟追數, 我怕佢淋我屋企紅油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋係怕搞到俾隔離啲鄰居鄙視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbdb694649da3ad3e6df56503ce872f7e85e0dd9","tid":584053,"uid":42767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T13:56:21.000Z","msg":"差得幾千蚊，未計人工罐油都成舊幾兩舊水<br />\n你係果啲收數公司員工/老細會唔會咁高成本同風險黎收咁細條數"},{"pid":"b1d94e5682a3f654f7ce1813f3f7c8e22a01d1de","tid":584053,"uid":38946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T13:58:12.000Z","msg":"安x ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13673c16ba326cf0c4e2c09752c8035a07a87b8","tid":584053,"uid":3186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cbdb694649da3ad3e6df56503ce872f7e85e0dd9","tid":584053,"uid":42767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T13:56:21.000Z","msg":"差得幾千蚊，未計人工罐油都成舊幾兩舊水<br />\n你係果啲收數公司員工/老細會唔會咁高成本同風險黎收咁細條數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:05:01.000Z","msg":"我寄完一次又一次呀<br />\n見到果下真係影響晒成家人心情<br />\n食飯都靜蠅蠅<br />\n心血小真係唔嚇得"},{"pid":"753852fc1a0ef96165a284675b628a52b799373b","tid":584053,"uid":3186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1d94e5682a3f654f7ce1813f3f7c8e22a01d1de","tid":584053,"uid":38946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T13:58:12.000Z","msg":"安x ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:07:43.000Z","msg":"唔清楚啲財仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗出名果堆應該唔會寄咁Hea嘅信掛<br />\n<br />\n無上下款無電話<br />\n得個印傭人頭樣, 金額同埋blur 咗某啲位嘅身份證<br />\n我老豆想打電話屌柒佢都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ccb201d5ac6d47e46d2728d2f2a08554f94b18a","tid":584053,"uid":99397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:15:12.000Z","msg":"貼上呢睇下，可能係流"},{"pid":"2583abf23771a4d924162d3b0917c340b7e8033d","tid":584053,"uid":3186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ccb201d5ac6d47e46d2728d2f2a08554f94b18a","tid":584053,"uid":99397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:15:12.000Z","msg":"貼上呢睇下，可能係流"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:26:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e066486c401b73a9c577a26a9d5c906cab56d1ae","tid":584053,"uid":84867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:44:25.000Z","msg":"驚佢條毛咩，果幾千蚊數，佢得鳩閑派人上黎淋你紅油咩，請人上門車馬費飲茶灌水唔駛錢呀，仲未計買油錢，你估平呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}